      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊表示，股市落后者应迎头赶上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/strategist-who-foresaw-stock-selloff-says-laggards-due-a-catchup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾预见到上个月市场调整的摩根士丹利策略师表示，如果周五公布的数据能够进一步证明经济具有韧性，那么落后于美国股市涨势的股票可能会得到提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/strategist-who-foresaw-stock-selloff-says-laggards-due-a-catchup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Illumina 赢得与欧盟就 70 亿美元 Grail 收购案的诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/illumina-grail-deal-was-wrongly-probed-by-eu-top-court-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最高法院的一项裁决，欧盟本不应该对 Illumina Inc. 以 70 亿美元收购癌症检测提供商 Grail Inc. 的交易进行调查，该裁决对欧盟审查更多全球交易的努力造成了重大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/illumina-grail-deal-was-wrongly-probed-by-eu-top-court-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 07:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
